  letterText: {fileID: 755935096}
  message: 'To the last Knight,


    A great shadow has fallen upon our kingdom.

    The
    dark wizard Velaryo has corrupted the royal castle, and his forbidden magic has
    torn open a portal to a demonic realm.


    From this portal he summons monstrous
    creatures that threaten to overrun the land...'
